               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1341" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1341" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1341" type="surname" value="ARCHER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1341" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ARCHER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 150.) On the 21 it of May I saw the prisoners together in Greenwich fair—they went behind a gentleman and tried his pocket, but found nothing—I saw them afterwards go behind the prosecutor—Pratt felt in his pocket, then went back and spoke to Chaplin, who closed up to the prosecutor, Pratt covering him—Chaplin pat his hand into the prosecutor's left coat-tail pocket, and drew this hand<lb></lb>kerchief—I immediately took hold of him, and took it from his hand—I secured them both.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PHILLIPS</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Are you sure you can make no mistake about this? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Quite—there were a good many persons in the fair—I had never seen Chaplin before—I took them on the spot, before they moved a step.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1342" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1342" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1342" type="surname" value="BURNS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1342" type="given" value="PATRICK"></interp>PATRICK BURNS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a labourer, and live in Commerial-road, Lam<lb></lb>beth. This is my handkerchief—I had it in my pocket at Greenwich fair, on Tuesday, the 21st of May—I was looking at a show—the officer tapped me on the shoulder, and asked if that handkerchief was mine, and I said it was—he had hold of the prisoners—I did not feel it taken.</p>
               <p>(Chaplin received a good character.)</p>
